---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Kya Hai Yeh RealityCheck? — RealityCheck Tools" description="Humne RealityCheck.tools banaya hai taki tu apni aadaton ka sach sun sake. Bina matlab ke.">
  <div class="section-padding" style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding-top:48px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:48px;">Kya Hai Yeh RealityCheck?</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:16px;margin-bottom:32px;">Humne banaya kyunki koi aur tujhe sach nahi batata.</p>
    <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:var(--space-xl);text-align:left;">
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:15px;">Roz chhoti-chhoti choices jo bade consequences mein badal jaati hain. Coffee yahan, subscription wahan, soone se pehle ek ghanta scroll. Ek-tok koi baat nahi. Lekin saath mein? Toh life decide karti hain.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:15px;">RealityCheck.tools ek collection hai - bina matlab ke honest calculators jo dikhate hain teri aadaton ki asli keemat. Na sugarcoating. Na sympathy. Bas sach, aur thoda sarcasm.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;font-size:15px;">Hum maante hain ki change awareness se aata hai. Kabhi kabhi kisi aur ko tujhe uncomfortable sach bolna padta hai. Hum woh "kuch" hain. 5 different tones ke saath — Friendly se Indian Parent tak — jo guilt chahiye, woh lo.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:32px;"><a href="/" class="btn-primary">Sach Suno</a></div>
  </div>
</Layout>
